data.description: San Antonio MEPS (Military Entrance Processing Station) is where individuals are processed for enlistment or induction into the armed services, based on DoD-approved peacetime and mobilization standards. In 2015, the USO was graciously invited to provide an area for individuals and families while going through the enlistment process. We provide a Home Away from Home for many who are away from home for the first time. They can get a hot cup of coffee, a cool beverage, a snack, or simply relax before the next step in this process.
